{"id":441596,"date":[{"year":1963,"month":3,"day":24}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"149","ytitle":"","mtitle":"夜垦歌","ftitle":"","authors":["陈忠干"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士　陈忠干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜垦的机群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘎嘎嘎嘎地响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车灯一划一划，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把夜幕点亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥香风香柴油香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春夜醉倒望苇荡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苇地似雁群咕噜咕噜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着犁铧飞翔、飞翔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜垦的机群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘎嘎嘎嘎地响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它伴着大海的节奏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤醒了千年的荒滩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的声音象春天的曲子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的海岛在歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘎嘎嘎嘎，嘎嘎嘎嘎嘎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱出一个农场，又一个农场……"}]}